  <brief_title>A Two Week Dosing Study to Determine the Safety and Antiviral Activity of LCQ908 in Hepatitis C Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Multi-center Trial, to Determine the Safety and Antiviral Effect of 14 Days of LCQ908 Monotherapy in Hepatitis C Infected Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
